ED_Title: Proposed programme  of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) for the eightieth session of the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 47th plenary meeting, on 4 December 2024, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee),  (Footnote: A/79/432.), approved the proposed programme of work and timetable of the Fourth Committee for the eightieth session of the Assembly, as set out in the report of the Committee.  (Footnote: A/79/432.)
